reviewText: This is a really funny story/movie, which I saw over 40 years ago on television.  The problem was that the picture and sound quality of this copy was so bad that I suspect it was filmed in a theater many years ago with an 8 mm. camera, then transferred to videotape.

The only reason I bought this movie, it had Raquel Welch in it. This had a very young Raquel in it and she look great. Outside of that this movie was bad. It was about a guy who thinks he saw a murder. He also thinks that Raquel saw the murder also and that's when the movie goes down hill and fast.
